            "id": 6327676,
            "title": "外資變臉賣超512億元 大砍面板三虎20萬張 元月買超僅88億元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>台股今 (30) 日跌逾 400 點，失守 5 日線並回測 3 萬 2 千點關卡，外資由連 3 買轉為賣超 512 億元，大砍面板三虎共逾 20 萬張，也砍台積電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2330:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2330\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2330-TW</a>)1.37 萬張、反手敲進力積電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6770:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6770\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6770-TW</a>) 近 7.7 萬張最多。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" src=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/6327676/l/8618a2523b0a3ae18a7a9564a0d762f3.jpg\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">外資變臉賣超512億元 大砍面板三虎20萬張 元月買超僅88億元。(鉅亨網資料照)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>台股元月大漲 3100 點，並一度逼近 3 萬 3000 點歷史新高，上演史上最強元月行情，不過三大法人在指數高檔的操作以調節為主，全月賣超 962 億元，其中投信賣超 1182 億元，外資僅買超 88 億元、自營商買超 132 億元。</p></section><section>\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>外資今日賣超最多為群創 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3481:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3481\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3481-TW</a>) 15.65 萬張，以及友達 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2409:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2409\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2409-TW</a>) 3.89 萬張、彩晶 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6116:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6116\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6116-TW</a>) 7,847 張。除了砍台積電外，外資也賣超鴻海 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2317:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2317\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2317-TW</a>) 1.36 萬張、宏碁 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2353:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2353\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2353-TW</a>) 1.24 萬張、佳能 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2374:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2374\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2374-TW</a>) 1.02 萬張等電子股。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>非電族群方面，外資賣超較多的金融股為兆豐金 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2886:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2886\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2886-TW</a>) 1.99 萬張、永豐金 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2890:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2890\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2890-TW</a>) 1.33 萬張；傳產則有大成鋼 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2027:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2027\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2027-TW</a>) 1.3 萬張、中石化 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1314:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1314\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1314-TW</a>) 1.06 萬張；ETF 賣超元大台灣 50(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:0050:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/0050\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">0050-TW</a>) 6.37 萬張較多。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>在記憶體族群方面，外資雖然賣超旺宏 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2337:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2337\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2337-TW</a>) 2.67 萬張及華邦電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2344:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2344\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2344-TW</a>) 1.87 萬張，但反手買超力積電，也買超南亞科 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2408:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2408\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2408-TW</a>) 2.11 萬張，以及南茂 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:8150:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8150\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8150-TW</a>) 6,877 張、華泰 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2329:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2329\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2329-TW</a>) 4,282 張、至上 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:8112:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8112\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8112-TW</a>) 1.39 萬張。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>此外，外資也買超聯電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2303:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2303\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2303-TW</a>) 5.19 萬張、PCB 的燿華 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2367:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2367\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2367-TW</a>) 2.43 萬張、華通 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2313:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2313\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2313-TW</a>) 5,488 張，以及仁寶 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2324:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2324\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2324-TW</a>) 7,039 張、康舒 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6282:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6282\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6282-TW</a>) 6,052 張等電子股。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>外資買超的傳產則有可寧衛 *(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:8422:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8422\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8422-TW</a>) 1.93 萬張、華新 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1605:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1605\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1605-TW</a>) 1.07 萬張、中鋼 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2002:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2002\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2002-TW</a>) 9,709 張，以及旗下中鴻 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2014:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2014\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2014-TW</a>) 3,863 張、華航 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2610:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2610\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2610-TW</a>) 8,863 張等，金融股則以凱基金 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2883:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2883\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2883-TW</a>) 9,550 張較多。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
